    "name": "HubSpot CRM Search API",
    "description": "The CRM Search API allows you to query and filter CRM objects using a flexible search interface. You can search across contacts, companies, deals, tickets, and other object types using filter groups, sorts, and pagination. Each search request targets a specific object type.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: HubSpot Developer Support",
